# Wingstop GX — environment

# Required for Lil Ranchie (WS2). The chatbot calls the Claude API for NLU/voice;
# the deterministic policy engine (lib/domain/policy.ts) owns every money decision.
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com — or run `ant auth login`.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional — model override. Defaults to claude-opus-4-8.
# For a snappier guest chat you can switch to claude-sonnet-4-6.
# RANCHIE_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8
